  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.2">
<l>vaippā maruntā maṭiyarai valviṉait</l>
<l>tuppām pulaṉaintun tuñcak koṭāṉava</l>
<l>ṉeppā levarkku nalattā luyarntuyarn</l>
<l>tappāla vaṉeṅka ḷāyar koḻuntē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The treasure is he, the remedy is he who does not permit</l>
<l>[his] severants harsh karma so that the five sense sleep that are the force [of it].</l>
<l>Ascending [and] ascending through goodness of everyone in every part</l>
<l>he is of that part, our sprout of the cowherd clan.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
